goal:
Established in 1998, Quantlab is a leading quantitative trading firm active in more than 40 markets around the world including pan European markets.

Quantlab believes that fair, efficient and competitive public markets best serve investors and promotes these principles through its education efforts.
interests: Banking and financial services, Competition, Economy, finance and the euro, Single market, Taxation
